=Description=

"The Fundación de los Comunes is a project driven by various experiences of autonomous research, education, publishing and political intervention practiced in social movements in Spain (Barcelona, Madrid, Málaga, Terrassa, Donosti..). Our aim is to think through models of a commons based institutionality that would be able to guarantee the ongoing development of radical critical production. Inside this frame, common goods and the social commoning movements to defend social rights, are a central sphere of our action and critical production."
(Commonswatch mailing list, November 2016)

